data.description: This property is situated in the highly sought-after Carolina Plantation, offering both convenience and popularity. With 4 bedrooms and 2 1/2 bathrooms, this house provides ample space for comfortable living. The lower level features an open living room-kitchen combination, along with a separate formal dining area that can also be utilized as an office space. Additionally, there is a half bath downstairs for added convenience. Upstairs, you will find four generously sized bedrooms. The Master Suite is particularly impressive, boasting a spacious layout that allows for the expression of your unique design style. It includes a Walk-in closet, double vanity, walk-in shower, garden tub, and water closet, providing a luxurious and functional retreat.The backyard of this property is expansive and is enclosed by a sturdy and well-maintained fence. It offers a generous amount of space, allowing for various outdoor activities and recreational opportunities. The fence provides privacy and security, creating a peaceful and secluded atmosphere. With its size, the backyard presents endless possibilities for gardening, hosting gatherings, or simply enjoying leisurely moments outdoors. Whether you envision a play area for children, a tranquil oasis for relaxation, or a space for entertaining guests, this big fenced-in backyard can accommodate your desires and provide a safe and enjoyable outdoor haven.
